Dear All Interns,

Please note that the Intern Leave and Conduct Policy (POL001) has been updated effective January 1, 2025 (version 3.0).

Key changes:
1. Medical leave increased from 1 day to 2 days per internship period
2. Work from home now permitted with mentor approval
3. Completion bonus increased to Rs 5,000

Please read the full policy document available on the HR portal.

